Q2:
Count word frequencies.
Input
["cat","dog","cat","bird","dog","cat"]

Output

{
    cat: 3,
    dog: 2,
    bird: 1
}
solution: (needed help revising syntax )
let x = ["cat","dog","cat","bird","dog","cat"]
const obj = {};


for (const animal of x) {
    obj[animal] = (obj[animal] || 0) + 1;
}

console.log(obj);

